  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/09-21-2023-release-updates\">Released 09/21/2023</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://support.liferay.com/documents/d/customer-portal/19940499255437-mceclip0\"><br>\nIn the latest update, we've enhanced the visibility and accessibility of the </span><code>LCP.json</code><span> configurations for each build on the Liferay Cloud platform. Users can now directly view the </span><code>LCP.json</code><span> file for any build, aiding in easier troubleshooting and configuration verification. For added convenience, the interface provides options to download the configuration, copy it to the clipboard, or deploy a successful build. This update aims to streamline the user experience and expedite the support process.</span></p>"
      },
